text: Walter Patrick Bexigas Ramos Lopes (born 10 August 1992 in Lisbon) is a Portuguese footballer who most recently played for FC Hradec Králové as a forward.Hradec? Jistá je posila z Příbrami a Krmaš jedná s dalšími třemi hráči. Novou tvář bude mít i realizační tým‚ efotbal.cz, 2 January 2018 ==Football career== On 10 May 2015, Walter Patrick made his professional debut with Oliveirense in a 2014–15 Segunda Liga match against Farense. ==References== ==External links== *Stats and profile at Zerozero * *Stats and profile at LPFP * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Lisbon Category:Portuguese footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:LigaPro players Category:Associação Naval 1º de Maio players Category:U.D.
